				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok last night my group took this guy with only minor difficutly. Here's what happened:<BR>
<BR>
We beamed up through the mirror and were instantly attacked by him. I had difficulty getting my pet (necro 48) up because for some reason he really really liked me. After my he got off me I managed to get my pet up and send him into battle. Our group consisted of the following, 46 Warrior, 42 Ranger, 42 Wizard, 40 Shammy, 53 cleric and myself 48 necro. He was one mean SoB. Lots of DOT's and very MONK style fighting..the thing about his health..ya its ALOT but I managaed to hit him with Asystole and Chilling embrace so hes regen wasn't helping him much. After what seemed to be about 5-10 min, and he blinds and he dots so be careful, he finally died. We did not see any bats, nor did he Gate so we must have got lucky. If you go up there and you are not ready..AND he has his little buddies with him, it will be very difficult. We are going back tonight to explore further. We are loving this tower and if you have high enough levels theres lots of loot and xp to be gotten in here. Just be careful.<BR>
